<H3> <TI>   Edict, Statute on Changes to, Review of `Citizenship Questions' </TI></H3>
<H4>   Text of Edict </H4>
<F P=102> 944F0275A Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 22 Jan 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> 944F0275A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:CSO 

<F P=106> ["Edict of the President of the Russian Federation `On </F>
Making Changes and Additions to the Statute on the Procedure for 
Consideration of Questions of Citizenship in the Russian 
Federation'"] 
  [Text] In connection with the adoption of the Law of the 
Russian Federation "On Making Changes and Additions to the Law 
of the RSFSR `On RSFSR Citizenship,'" I decree: 
  1. Changes and additions shall be made to the Statute on the 
Procedure for Consideration of Questions of Citizenship in the 
Russian Federation, approved by the Edict of the President of 
the Russian Federation of 10 April 1992 No. 386 (VEDOMOSTI 
SYEZDA NARODNYKH DEPUTATOV I VERKHOVNOGO SOVETA ROSSIYSKOY 
FEDERATSII, 1992, No. 17, p. 952), set forth with new wording 
(appended). 
  2. The present edict shall take effect on the day of its 
publication. 
  [Signed] President of the Russian Federation B. Yeltsin 
  the Kremlin, Moscow 
  27 December 1993 
  No. 2299 

</TEXT>

