<H3> <TI>   Energy Sector Strikes Threatened </TI></H3>
<H4>   Komi Oil Fields </H4>
<F P=102> 944E0415B Moscow RABOCHAYA TRIBUNA in Russian 29 Jan 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 944E0415B </F>
